Slug
====

Slugs columns, adds a slug finder and sets to_param for slug models. Requires a 'slug' field in the database, where the slug itself is stored.


Example
=======

 class Post < ActiveRecord::Base
   has_slug # defaults to title
 end

 class Document < ActiveRecord::Base
   has_slug :filename
 end


